  "text": "Several phenomena have been identified that are effective in providing a powerful cardioprotection, such as ischemic preconditioning (IPC) [CITATION_1] ), ischemic postconditioning [CITATION_2] , remote ischemic conditioning [CITATION_3] ) and pharmacological preconditioning [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
